            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "And, if the basic human decency of supporting women through this isn't enough for employers, there's a significant impact on productivity of those impacted by harassment ‚Äî with 2% leaving journalism entirely. ",
